metadata.name: Scrutinize
metadata.description:
Woman#4 story "Eva"

Part 5 of 7

What else could she do but suffer? What else? Burst, Eva, burst with sadness. Erase evil by the square root of your volatile existence. Eva, what else to do but chase, watch over and die? Eva didn't know what to do with her sadness. She dissected through every memory, every event, every decision, looking for something that could be the cause. Nothing found.
